cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.IT, cs.CY

The paper proposes a model for predicting passenger origin-destination in intelligent transportation systems, which involves machine learning and data analysis techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper deals with optimization and information theory, which could place it in cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.CY (Cryptography and Security).
